Let \( X \) be a random variable having a probability density function \( f \in \{f_0, f_1\} \), where
\[f_0(x) = 
\begin{cases} 
1, & \text{if } 0 \leq x \leq 1 \\
0, & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}\]
and
\[f_1(x) = 
\begin{cases} 
\frac{1}{2}, & \text{if } 0 \leq x \leq 2 \\
0, & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}.\]
